sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice
    participant Bob
    participant Carol

    Alice->>Bob: solid sync arrow
    Bob-->>Alice: dashed return
    Alice->Bob: open arrow (no head)
    Bob--xAlice: cross terminated
    Alice->>+Bob: activate on receive
    Bob-->>-Alice: deactivate on send
    Alice->>Carol: parallel message
    Carol-->>Alice: parallel return
